name: Mikey's Place Bar & Restaurant

reviews.review_text: The menu we found on Google Maps was different from the actual one, and the food was quite costly. However, the taste and environment were good. The Chicken Cafreal and Squid Batter Fry stood out as delicious. The complimentary dessert was a nice touch, and Schubert, the waiter, had great behavior and service. Decent experience overall!
A cozy spot serving delicious Goan and Indian dishes for years. Loved the flavorful Pomfret Masala Fry perfectly spiced and fresh. Great food with a warm, welcoming vibe!

Never have I had a more pleasant meal.The guy who looked after us Alister was so polite and helpful, going above and beyond to make us feel welcome. Dinner experience with great atmosphere.the Dragon chicken chilly and chicken steak in pepper sauce was so yummy, even though it was quite heavy for one person. Perfectly cooked and the flavor and served with mash potatoes and veggies. There was live music which made my mood so so good and  dessert Cheesecake with blueberry sauce which taste really good.

description:
Mikey’s Place Bar & Restaurant, nestled in the Corlim Industrial Estate, shines brightly with an impressive rating of 4.8 from a substantial crowd of 16,882 reviews. This beloved eatery has garnered accolades for its sumptuous Goan cuisine, making it a popular haunt for locals and visitors alike. Customers frequently highlight specialties such as the *Chicken Cafreal* and *Serradura*, while the delightful live music and cozy atmosphere complement the vibrant dining experience.

### Ambiance & Design
Upon entering Mikey’s Place, diners are greeted by a warm and inviting ambiance. The décor balances modern touches with traditional Goan charm, offering a cozy yet lively environment. The lighting is soft, creating a perfect backdrop for enjoying meals with family and friends. Customer photos capture not just the delicious dishes but also the atmosphere—several images showcase intimate seating arrangements adorned with local art, highlighting the establishment's commitment to local culture. Patrons revel in the presence of live music, which infuses the space with an upbeat yet relaxed vibe, ideal for celebrating special occasions or simply enjoying a night out.

### Menu & Culinary Experience
The menu at Mikey’s Place reflects its dedication to authentic Goan and Indian flavors. Signature dishes like *Pomfret Masala Fry* and *Dragon Chicken Chilly* have received notable praise for their bold flavors and exquisite preparation. Each dish is presented impeccably; for instance, the *Chicken Steak in Pepper Sauce*, accompanied by mashed potatoes and seasonal veggies, is visually appealing as much as it is delicious. The addition of complimentary desserts, like the popular *Cheesecake with Blueberry Sauce* and *Serradura*, showcases the restaurant's flair for making meals unforgettable. Even though some diners noted mismatches between online menus and the actual offerings, the overall satisfaction regarding taste and presentation remains remarkably high.

### Customer Experience & Service
Service at Mikey’s Place is an evident strong suit. Guests consistently mention the attentiveness of the staff, particularly praising individual servers like Schubert and Alister for their welcoming demeanor and accommodating service. Reviews note that diners feel genuinely cared for, enjoying personalized attention that enhances their overall experience. The restaurant appears to maintain a relaxed reservation policy, inviting both reservations and walk-in guests, though the latter might experience a wait due to the restaurant’s popularity.

### Popularity & Reviews
Mikey's Place has established itself as a beloved destination, with countless positive sentiments resonating in customer reviews. Recurring praise for the *Goan food*, particularly the *murad* and *band*, highlights its specialization in the region's culinary traditions. The combination of delicious food, friendly service, and an engaging environment has solidified this restaurant's reputation across social media platforms as well, making it a must-visit. While the establishment has yet to earn notable critic ratings or awards that echo its popularity, the enthusiastic feedback from patrons conveys a strong community endorsement.

### Utilizing Visual Content
Visual content plays a pivotal role in communicating the charm and culinary delights of Mikey’s Place. The images provided by customers vividly showcase the beautifully plated dishes, the inviting seating, and the overall ambiance of the restaurant—each snapshot tells a story of satisfied diners immersed in an enjoyable dining experience. From the enticing presentation of the *Squid Batter Fry* to the heartwarming display of numerous guests enjoying their meals, these visuals enhance the narrative of this dynamic culinary haven.

In conclusion, Mikey’s Place Bar & Restaurant emerges as a culinary gem in Corlim, promising a delightful experience through its renowned Goan dishes, exceptional service, and inviting atmosphere. Whether you're a local or a traveler, a meal here seems not only to satisfy the taste buds but also to create lasting memories.
